WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 23=

02:52.670 --> 02:55.020
Greetings, Your Grace.

03:08.700 --> 03:09.900
In the end, she had no choice

03:09.900 --> 03:11.180
but to take up the Kunwu Blade

03:11.830 --> 03:13.950
and become the Sovereign of Spirits

03:14.550 --> 03:15.670
feared by all spirits,

03:15.670 --> 03:17.300
following the same path as her father.

03:21.610 --> 03:26.460
♪Spirits are intoxicated♪

03:26.630 --> 03:30.280
♪With obsessions♪

03:33.060 --> 03:38.010
♪Forget the form to achieve♪

03:38.230 --> 03:42.180
♪Yet I can't♪

03:44.750 --> 03:49.770
♪Today, a home is granted♪

03:50.430 --> 03:55.570
♪Joy without grief♪

03:56.250 --> 04:01.290
♪Lanterns light the empty delusions♪

04:01.290 --> 04:05.850
♪All are ferried across♪

04:07.940 --> 04:12.790
♪Spirits are intoxicated♪

04:12.960 --> 04:15.500
♪With obsessions♪

04:15.510 --> 04:17.260
Greetings, Your Grace.

04:22.380 --> 04:24.500
Ever since Simu became the Sovereign,

04:24.560 --> 04:26.850
♪Yet I can't♪

04:26.860 --> 04:29.060
rather, after her parents left,

04:29.990 --> 04:31.350
she changed completely.

04:32.420 --> 04:34.060
Even I found her a stranger.

04:35.350 --> 04:37.350
She was no longer who she once was.

04:38.350 --> 04:40.470
To keep herself on guard at all times,

04:41.350 --> 04:43.470
it was not only her body and flesh;

04:44.380 --> 04:45.740
she even made her heart

04:46.060 --> 04:47.740
turn utterly cold and ruthless.

04:47.740 --> 04:52.180
♪All are ferried across♪

04:52.180 --> 04:54.500
(Sovereign's Hall)

04:55.300 --> 04:56.500
Over these four hundred years,

04:56.910 --> 04:58.820
Simu has done so much for the Mortal

04:59.060 --> 05:00.030
and Spirit Worlds.

05:00.740 --> 05:02.910
But no one has truly reached her,

05:03.110 --> 05:03.950
understood her,

05:04.300 --> 05:05.380
or done anything for her.

05:06.820 --> 05:08.820
Then again, she has no need of it,

05:09.350 --> 05:10.230
nor does she expect us

05:10.230 --> 05:11.420
to give anything for her.

05:12.860 --> 05:15.150
After all, powerful as she is,

05:16.110 --> 05:17.230
there is little we can do

05:17.230 --> 05:18.470
for her.

05:21.150 --> 05:22.030
I see.

05:24.790 --> 05:26.300
She's long accepted her fate:

05:28.790 --> 05:29.790
Born only to die,

05:31.300 --> 05:32.300
she endures eternity.

05:34.990 --> 05:36.500
All she loves fades like smoke.

05:38.380 --> 05:39.420
Only the abyss will endure

05:41.350 --> 05:42.230
as long as she does.

05:43.990 --> 05:44.830
Why?

05:45.060 --> 05:46.180
Are you afraid?

05:51.910 --> 05:53.180
Simu is a very stubborn girl.

05:54.110 --> 05:55.230
From her parents,

05:55.860 --> 05:57.820
she inherited an unbreakable pride.

05:58.060 --> 05:58.940
She warms this world

05:59.260 --> 06:00.100
with her fervor.

06:00.500 --> 06:01.806
That is exactly why I adore her.

06:03.820 --> 06:04.660
Your Ladyship,

06:05.420 --> 06:06.260
am I the first one

06:06.260 --> 06:07.260
to come out of the Prison

06:07.550 --> 06:08.670
with my soul candle

06:08.670 --> 06:09.510
being snuff out?

06:09.710 --> 06:11.260
You are the first mortal to do it.

06:12.030 --> 06:13.940
But the first spirit

06:13.940 --> 06:14.910
was Simu.

06:15.470 --> 06:17.500
The two most powerful spirits
in the Void,

06:17.990 --> 06:18.830
Simu and that one,

06:19.470 --> 06:20.543
once clashed in the Prison.

06:20.860 --> 06:22.910
Both their soul candles went out.

06:23.740 --> 06:25.350
Yet Simu alone, three days later,

06:25.990 --> 06:27.590
walked back out

06:27.590 --> 06:28.430
and relit

06:28.440 --> 06:29.300
the soul candle.

06:29.710 --> 06:30.670
It was a miracle.

06:32.860 --> 06:33.860
As expected of Simu.

06:33.977 --> 06:35.350
One free of desire stands unshaken.

06:35.590 --> 06:36.710
Spirits are bound

06:36.710 --> 06:37.990
by the obsessions they cling to,

06:38.260 --> 06:39.260
so they can't break free

06:39.260 --> 06:40.590
from the Prison's illusions.

06:41.150 --> 06:42.230
But Simu is different.

06:42.620 --> 06:44.860
Obsession isn't what makes her;

06:45.420 --> 06:47.060
love is.

06:51.350 --> 06:52.190
It is still early.

06:53.500 --> 06:55.910
Your Ladyship, tell me more.

06:57.670 --> 06:58.510
Gladly.

06:58.790 --> 06:59.630
If you want,

06:59.793 --> 07:00.940
I can talk without repetition

07:00.940 --> 07:02.006
for three days and nights.

07:07.230 --> 07:08.070
Simu.

07:08.260 --> 07:09.300
I've heard much about you.

07:10.230 --> 07:11.230
I didn't expect you...

07:11.230 --> 07:12.550
Now that you are out of bed,

07:13.380 --> 07:14.820
come with me.

07:16.030 --> 07:16.870
All right.

07:17.670 --> 07:18.510
Where are we going?

07:21.740 --> 07:22.790
Just come with me.

07:24.620 --> 07:29.740
(Graveyard on the Void Mountain,
the Void)

07:30.030 --> 07:30.870
Simu,

07:32.030 --> 07:32.870
this place is...

07:33.710 --> 07:34.790
Over 400 years,

07:35.550 --> 07:37.230
I've had 22 lovers.

07:38.470 --> 07:39.500
These are their graves.

07:41.060 --> 07:42.060
Most of them never knew

07:42.060 --> 07:43.060
who I really was.

07:44.550 --> 07:46.110
The time I spent with them

07:47.100 --> 07:47.940
was on and off,

07:47.940 --> 07:49.180
yet it totaled only 20 years.

07:51.790 --> 07:53.620
This is the first mortal I ever liked

07:54.910 --> 07:56.550
before my father was annihilated.

07:58.380 --> 07:59.220
Wherever

08:00.150 --> 08:01.260
our journey took us,

08:02.500 --> 08:03.590
he followed me there.

08:06.030 --> 08:06.870
His name was...

08:16.180 --> 08:17.020
I can't remember.

08:17.740 --> 08:19.300
I once cared for him deeply,

08:21.590 --> 08:22.440
but now,

08:22.440 --> 08:23.360
I can't even speak

08:23.360 --> 08:24.210
his name aloud.

08:26.300 --> 08:27.140
Duan Xu,

08:29.380 --> 08:30.550
this is who I am.

08:32.830 --> 08:34.780
My life is measured in centuries.

08:35.990 --> 08:37.710
Time will wear everything away.

08:40.070 --> 08:40.930
One day,

08:40.940 --> 08:41.860
I won't even

08:41.860 --> 08:42.700
remember your name,

08:43.950 --> 08:44.860
let alone

08:44.860 --> 08:46.430
the grand tales behind you

08:47.140 --> 08:48.830
or the memories we once shared.

08:51.990 --> 08:53.470
How long could you stay with me?

08:54.950 --> 08:55.790
In the end,

08:59.540 --> 09:00.489
you will be nothing more

09:00.500 --> 09:01.500
than a tiny ripple

09:02.470 --> 09:04.110
in my everlasting life.

09:06.310 --> 09:07.230
Would you

09:09.740 --> 09:10.710
accept that?

09:26.900 --> 09:28.140
It seems

09:28.140 --> 09:28.990
you genuinely like me.

09:30.620 --> 09:31.660
So, I'm genuinely

09:31.660 --> 09:32.500
rejecting you.

09:35.070 --> 09:35.950
Foxy,

09:38.070 --> 09:39.110
you have your dreams.

09:39.780 --> 09:41.430
Your first 20 years were too hard.

09:43.590 --> 09:45.620
From now on,
you should live more happily.

09:47.230 --> 09:48.950
You'll meet a girl you love more,

09:50.710 --> 09:51.740
start a family,

09:53.540 --> 09:54.590
and live a happy life,

09:54.830 --> 09:56.190
with kin you can lean on.

09:58.070 --> 09:59.900
I know you may be heartbroken now.

10:01.260 --> 10:02.190
But in a few months,

10:02.190 --> 10:03.070
you'll let it go.

10:04.470 --> 10:05.620
General Duan,

10:06.070 --> 10:07.190
you're a gifted young hero.

10:07.950 --> 10:09.590
What fine lady could you not wed?

10:10.990 --> 10:12.123
Go back to the Mortal World.

10:12.540 --> 10:13.540
If trouble finds you,

10:13.740 --> 10:14.990
or if you need any help,

10:15.470 --> 10:16.660
just call my name,

10:17.070 --> 10:17.910
and I will come.

10:19.070 --> 10:19.910
Of course.

10:20.500 --> 10:21.760
I wouldn't help you for nothing.

10:22.983 --> 10:25.036
I still have to trade with you
for the five senses.

10:25.620 --> 10:27.470
Did you let me see the Void

10:31.710 --> 10:32.950
only because of our deal?

10:38.190 --> 10:39.030
No.

10:40.540 --> 10:41.430
It was my thanks.

10:42.950 --> 10:44.780
You let me feel that the Mortal World

10:45.900 --> 10:47.540
is better than I ever expected.

10:49.230 --> 10:50.620
So, this is my thanks to you.

10:58.500 --> 11:00.110
You went to Prison to save me yourself.

11:02.110 --> 11:03.059
While I was unconscious,

11:03.070 --> 11:03.910
you stayed by my side

11:04.950 --> 11:06.110
the whole time.

11:07.020 --> 11:08.053
Whenever I called for you,

11:10.230 --> 11:11.470
you would always hold my hand.

11:13.830 --> 11:14.670
No need to thank me.

11:16.140 --> 11:17.500
I brought you to the Void.

11:18.740 --> 11:20.060
It was only right that I do this.

11:20.260 --> 11:21.110
I kissed you.

11:21.860 --> 11:22.766
I held you in my arms.

11:23.430 --> 11:24.620
You never truly punished me.

11:25.380 --> 11:26.549
You knew I could handle much

11:26.560 --> 11:27.190
on my own,

11:28.780 --> 11:29.950
but whenever I asked you,

11:32.380 --> 11:33.453
you always went soft on me.

11:35.110 --> 11:36.996
You are good at pouting and pleading.

11:37.007 --> 11:38.133
Do not dodge the real issue.

11:38.260 --> 11:39.780
What issue am I dodging?

11:45.590 --> 11:46.430
Do you truly

11:49.140 --> 11:50.590
have no feelings for me?

11:55.110 --> 11:56.620
You are not in my thoughts.

11:58.310 --> 11:59.540
After all, soon enough,

12:01.740 --> 12:03.260
I will even forget your name.

12:16.470 --> 12:17.710
Cry if you want.

12:19.660 --> 12:21.070
Just don't cry in front of me.

12:21.990 --> 12:23.500
You are my only spell bearer.

12:24.950 --> 12:26.230
I hope all your wishes

12:26.230 --> 12:27.110
come true.

12:31.780 --> 12:33.660
But I am the wish you can't fulfill.

12:37.590 --> 12:38.620
Take me out

12:38.620 --> 12:39.460
of your wishes.

12:54.830 --> 12:56.110
May you grow wings

12:58.310 --> 12:59.470
and achieve your ambitions.

14:11.430 --> 14:12.710
She fears the sound of thunder.

14:19.310 --> 14:20.740
Now, I know her a little better.

14:28.990 --> 14:30.310
Bad timing.

14:33.190 --> 14:34.310
She's so cruel,

14:38.470 --> 14:39.310
isn't she?

14:53.500 --> 14:55.110
That's what you want, right?

14:56.020 --> 14:57.310
Just a mere mortal.

14:57.950 --> 14:59.140
I knew it would come to this.

14:59.710 --> 15:01.380
He is no mere mortal.

15:03.350 --> 15:04.540
This child is different.

15:05.740 --> 15:07.070
He truly understands Simu.

15:08.900 --> 15:10.070
What could he understand?

15:10.710 --> 15:13.470
Perhaps the things that you never

15:13.710 --> 15:15.590
managed to grasp in 300 years.

15:18.570 --> 15:19.410
You act

15:19.410 --> 15:20.900
as if you understand it all.

15:21.710 --> 15:22.990
Why can't you let Bai Sanxing go

15:23.260 --> 15:25.260
after 300 years?

15:25.540 --> 15:27.230
Worry about yourself first.

15:27.780 --> 15:29.350
Even if this mortal leaves,

15:29.590 --> 15:31.140
do you think Simu will choose you?

15:32.620 --> 15:33.830
Aren't you curious

15:34.710 --> 15:36.860
why Bai Sanxing's soul candle died out,

15:37.350 --> 15:38.350
yet after 300 years,

15:38.740 --> 15:40.020
he still hasn't met annihilation?

15:41.070 --> 15:42.660
That may sound simple enough,

15:43.310 --> 15:44.500
but there aren't many answers.

15:45.500 --> 15:47.190
His soul candle is still there.

15:49.780 --> 15:51.070
That's strange.

15:52.710 --> 15:53.950
Back then,

15:53.950 --> 15:54.860
we watched Simu

15:54.860 --> 15:56.860
snuff out his soul candle.

15:57.710 --> 15:59.470
That mortal's soul candle went out too,

16:00.110 --> 16:01.190
yet it was lit again.

16:04.620 --> 16:06.190
He could relight his soul candle,

16:06.830 --> 16:08.710
likely because he loved Simu deeply.

16:09.900 --> 16:11.350
As for Bai Sanxing...

16:14.020 --> 16:15.070
You suspect me?

16:15.470 --> 16:16.620
Bai Sanxing was madly

16:16.620 --> 16:17.620
in love with you.

16:18.140 --> 16:19.350
Everyone knew it.

16:21.230 --> 16:23.230
That's ancient history.

16:24.380 --> 16:25.830
Before he entered the Prison,

16:25.830 --> 16:27.350
he wanted me torn to pieces.

16:27.350 --> 16:29.110
Why would I light his soul candle?

16:29.900 --> 16:30.950
I'm not out of my mind.

16:36.590 --> 16:37.900
This is very strange.

16:38.660 --> 16:40.020
I'm afraid it may bring trouble.

16:43.190 --> 16:44.590
Tell me.

16:45.430 --> 16:47.260
Trouble for whom?

17:14.230 --> 17:15.230
(This young man)

17:15.740 --> 17:17.670
(is the most special mortal)

17:18.190 --> 17:19.430
(to me.)

17:23.020 --> 17:24.500
(On the battlefield, he was resolute,)

17:24.670 --> 17:25.950
(confident, and wildly proud.)

17:26.630 --> 17:28.430
(There was a self-destructive ferocity.)

17:29.630 --> 17:31.150
(His heart was shattered,)

17:31.670 --> 17:33.740
(with countless old scars,)

17:35.100 --> 17:37.100
(yet he gathered up
the fragments himself)

17:37.260 --> 17:38.470
(and pieced them back together)

17:38.630 --> 17:40.670
(till it beat with fierce,
living warmth.)

17:42.990 --> 17:44.500
(But only before me,)

17:45.820 --> 17:47.020
(when he spoke my name,)

17:47.390 --> 17:48.230
Simu.

17:48.300 --> 17:50.220
(he seemed like a wild beast,)

17:50.500 --> 17:51.990
(offering his throat and bare belly.)

17:53.540 --> 17:55.190
(That day when he was covered in blood,)

17:55.740 --> 17:57.300
(he did more than reach out to me.)

17:57.670 --> 17:59.300
(He placed his heart in my hands.)

18:02.990 --> 18:04.020
(From that moment on,)

18:05.190 --> 18:06.300
(the way he looked at me)

18:06.300 --> 18:07.190
(always seemed to say,)

18:08.020 --> 18:09.870
("You could wound me with ease.")

18:10.740 --> 18:12.060
("I've given you")

18:12.260 --> 18:13.260
("such power.")

18:15.430 --> 18:17.060
(Only now do I realize)

18:17.950 --> 18:19.340
(I was actually afraid.)

18:20.340 --> 18:22.230
This is the first time in my life

18:22.670 --> 18:23.910
that someone has come for me.

18:24.310 --> 18:26.170
♪Wander to the other shore
with the lantern♪

18:26.190 --> 18:28.100
(I'm afraid I can't hold this heart,)

18:28.820 --> 18:30.710
(and it will slip from my hands)

18:31.663 --> 18:32.780
(and shatter on the ground.)

18:32.780 --> 18:34.850
♪As all things turn and flow♪

18:34.850 --> 18:38.330
♪Whether I stay or go, I'm all alone♪

18:38.340 --> 18:39.190
(I want to shield him)

18:39.190 --> 18:40.910
(from the suffering
of the Mortal World,)

18:41.990 --> 18:44.020
(so this heart bears no new scars.)

18:48.390 --> 18:49.780
(For a mortal,)

18:51.020 --> 18:52.260
(the finest life is)

18:52.820 --> 18:54.340
(to rise with power)

18:54.820 --> 18:55.950
(and be happily married)

18:56.230 --> 18:57.300
(with kids)

18:57.820 --> 18:58.870
(and fulfilled ambitions,)

18:58.870 --> 19:02.520
♪A century is like a dream♪

19:02.710 --> 19:05.990
♪Let me journey across them all♪

19:06.260 --> 19:07.710
(instead of being entangled)

19:07.710 --> 19:08.723
(with a spirit like me.)

19:10.380 --> 19:13.900
♪A lone lamp shines on the other shore♪

19:13.950 --> 19:17.710
♪Accompanied by the abyss♪

19:17.960 --> 19:20.790
♪Moments may last♪

19:20.990 --> 19:26.810
♪Love and hate will fade away♪

19:26.820 --> 19:28.100
(I will return his heart)

19:30.470 --> 19:31.820
(to him intact.)

19:52.390 --> 19:53.390
Greetings, Your Lordship.

20:05.860 --> 20:07.260
(Ledger)

20:15.820 --> 20:16.740
This is the ledger

20:17.060 --> 20:18.910
Jiang Ai hid in Xuling Temple.

20:21.540 --> 20:22.380
Now,

20:23.820 --> 20:24.806
I place it in your hands.

20:30.340 --> 20:31.800
How are things with Jiang Ai?

20:32.470 --> 20:33.470
There is no movement yet.

20:34.470 --> 20:35.930
Though you're in charge

20:35.941 --> 20:37.147
of Jiang Ai's affairs for now,

20:37.710 --> 20:38.950
her influence still remains.

20:38.950 --> 20:40.020
Do not underestimate her.

20:41.540 --> 20:42.540
Now,

20:42.990 --> 20:44.300
she still trusts me.

20:44.910 --> 20:46.260
I may as well seize the chance

20:46.710 --> 20:47.550
and....

20:50.710 --> 20:52.300
Do not be too hasty.

20:53.630 --> 20:55.020
Once all is in readiness,

20:55.470 --> 20:57.630
I will bring her down for good

20:57.950 --> 20:59.950
and leave her no way back.

21:02.060 --> 21:03.300
When that time comes,

21:04.780 --> 21:05.950
I will have you

21:06.300 --> 21:07.340
take her place.

21:09.910 --> 21:11.100
You've always kept

21:11.950 --> 21:12.910
your promise to me.

21:14.150 --> 21:15.470
What do you want to do next?

21:15.670 --> 21:16.510
I can help you.

21:18.820 --> 21:20.060
There is one trouble indeed.

21:21.500 --> 21:22.580
I have received word

21:22.950 --> 21:23.950
that Bai Sanxing

21:24.430 --> 21:25.300
is still alive.

21:26.990 --> 21:28.020
Bai Sanxing?

21:28.430 --> 21:29.780
His spirit power is formidable.

21:30.060 --> 21:31.540
Even in the Prison,

21:31.540 --> 21:32.630
he managed to survive.

21:33.950 --> 21:36.300
One day, he will be a grave threat.

21:40.870 --> 21:41.710
I understand now.

21:43.430 --> 21:44.820
I will not let him live on.

21:58.020 --> 21:58.860
Your Lordship,

21:58.990 --> 22:00.470
that mortal has left the Void.

22:13.500 --> 22:16.060
I must have been half-asleep

22:16.630 --> 22:19.060
and opened the door by mistake.

22:20.740 --> 22:22.910
If Her Grace finds out,

22:23.190 --> 22:24.870
I will surely be punished.

22:25.870 --> 22:28.500
Good thing no one saw me.

22:40.580 --> 22:42.390
Always hiding here to read memorials.

22:42.820 --> 22:44.390
Since when did you grow so diligent?

22:47.390 --> 22:49.230
I just sent Mr. Duan away.

22:55.710 --> 22:58.100
He looked utterly heartbroken.

22:59.100 --> 22:59.940
Simu,

23:00.540 --> 23:01.420
don't you think

23:01.420 --> 23:02.470
you were too harsh on him?

23:06.870 --> 23:07.910
He left

23:07.910 --> 23:08.990
this gift for you.

23:09.190 --> 23:10.540
He asked me to deliver it to you.

23:10.740 --> 23:12.230
He said, "Take care."

23:39.500 --> 23:43.020
(Map of the Void)

23:50.660 --> 23:56.940
(Map of the Void)

24:01.940 --> 24:07.800
♪Touched memories linger like shadows♪

24:08.430 --> 24:13.940
♪Scattered reflections
sink into my heart♪

24:14.530 --> 24:16.490
♪If I could ♪

24:17.740 --> 24:20.100
(There is glowworm-like light here.)

24:21.340 --> 24:22.260
(In summer,)

24:22.780 --> 24:23.950
(it'd gleam in scattered,)

24:25.260 --> 24:26.150
(yellow-green lights)

24:27.340 --> 24:28.260
(like jade shining.)

24:30.540 --> 24:31.473
(As the ancients said,)

24:33.300 --> 24:34.600
(rain won't wash away the light;)

24:35.670 --> 24:36.803
(wind will only brighten it.)

24:38.390 --> 24:39.500
(If it were in the sky,)

24:40.870 --> 24:42.123
(it must be a star by the moon.)

24:43.720 --> 24:46.620
♪Hope we'll experience them together♪

24:47.220 --> 24:53.460
♪Before we forget or grow apart♪

24:54.740 --> 24:57.500
♪Even if the day gives way to night♪

24:57.500 --> 24:59.180
♪Grows dim and fades away♪

24:59.180 --> 25:01.980
♪What would come of it?♪

25:02.420 --> 25:03.900
♪I care for no one but you♪

25:03.900 --> 25:05.540
♪I'll come near and run to you♪

25:05.540 --> 25:08.740
♪To heal the deepest wounds♪

25:09.260 --> 25:11.850
♪Miracles, eternity, and radiance♪

25:11.870 --> 25:12.710
(For some reason,)

25:13.570 --> 25:14.316
(by the wall stood)

25:14.327 --> 25:15.600
(a cluster of rose-like plants.)

25:16.870 --> 25:17.843
(In the blooming season,)

25:18.836 --> 25:20.262
(their fragrance will fill the air;)

25:21.100 --> 25:22.190
(their thorns can wound;)

25:23.150 --> 25:24.630
(their crimson blooms vary in shade,)

25:26.060 --> 25:27.060
(like dawn and glow,)

25:28.780 --> 25:29.870
(set off well by plantain.)

25:31.540 --> 25:32.380
(As the saying goes,)

25:33.950 --> 25:36.260
(behind drawn curtains,
one naps at noon,)

25:37.390 --> 25:39.710
(with red rose trellis
and green plantain.)

25:39.870 --> 25:41.070
A Second-Place Scholar indeed.

25:42.500 --> 25:44.060
What a waste to use

25:44.950 --> 25:45.990
your gifts for this.

25:47.560 --> 25:53.130
♪A lifetime is given
for a name to be remembered♪

25:53.650 --> 25:56.500
♪There are passions and pains♪

25:56.540 --> 25:57.380
Scent,

25:57.990 --> 25:58.830
colors,

25:59.390 --> 26:00.230
and texture.

26:01.670 --> 26:02.665
Are you trying to give me

26:02.676 --> 26:03.580
a wholly different Void

26:03.580 --> 26:04.420
as your gift?

26:06.080 --> 26:07.900
♪Even if the day gives way to night♪

26:07.900 --> 26:09.100
♪Grows dim and fades away♪

26:09.100 --> 26:10.500
In this lonely place,

26:12.990 --> 26:15.150
do you mean to leave me life?

26:15.960 --> 26:18.660
♪To heal the deepest wounds♪

26:18.760 --> 26:19.940
Do you truly

26:19.940 --> 26:22.170
♪Miracles, eternity, and radiance♪

26:22.170 --> 26:23.720
have no feelings for me?

26:27.700 --> 26:30.170
♪Walking with you through eternity♪

26:30.190 --> 26:31.150
Foxy,

26:33.100 --> 26:34.910
why go to such trouble for me?

26:51.710 --> 26:52.580
Meng Wan.

26:52.580 --> 26:53.420
Qingsheng.

26:54.080 --> 26:54.703
- Xu.
- Xu.

26:54.714 --> 26:56.060
- Chenying.
- You're finally back.

26:56.060 --> 26:57.100
What are you doing here?

26:57.100 --> 26:57.940
Chenying.

26:58.870 --> 26:59.710
Look at you.

27:00.340 --> 27:01.260
You've become sturdier.

27:01.390 --> 27:02.990
Xu, you jest.

27:02.990 --> 27:04.150
It has only been a month.

27:04.150 --> 27:05.740
It's not that dramatic.

27:05.950 --> 27:06.790
General,

27:07.100 --> 27:07.940
long time no see.

27:08.340 --> 27:09.230
Xu,

27:09.230 --> 27:10.283
you've grown much thinner.

27:14.593 --> 27:15.670
How are things in the army?

27:15.670 --> 27:17.060
Rest easy, General. All is well.

27:17.340 --> 27:18.740
In three days, we'll reach Nandu.

27:19.150 --> 27:20.260
Where is Xiaoxiao?

27:20.540 --> 27:21.740
She didn't come back with you?

27:24.780 --> 27:25.620
She's fine.

27:27.100 --> 27:27.940
She went home.

27:29.990 --> 27:30.830
I should go home too.

27:34.390 --> 27:35.230
Chenying,

27:37.150 --> 27:38.103
let's go home together.

28:01.710 --> 28:02.550
Your Ladyship,

28:02.740 --> 28:03.740
what do you need?

28:04.380 --> 28:05.260
Gently.

28:05.260 --> 28:06.430
Find more male spirits.

28:06.780 --> 28:08.500
Send them all to the Left Hand?

28:08.820 --> 28:09.670
Yes.

28:09.680 --> 28:10.540
You will go as well.

28:12.670 --> 28:13.510
Yes, Your Ladyship.

28:21.180 --> 28:24.020
(Void Valley, the Void)

28:34.630 --> 28:36.060
Who's hiding here and playing tricks?

28:43.870 --> 28:44.710
My Lord, over there!

28:52.780 --> 28:53.620
Come out now.

29:25.940 --> 29:28.300
(Ascension Pool)

29:30.340 --> 29:32.300
Make sure the spirit set to jump

29:32.470 --> 29:34.870
into the pool matches the list.

29:35.300 --> 29:37.390
If there is another mismatch,

29:37.670 --> 29:38.945
jump down yourselves and make up

29:38.956 --> 29:39.660
the number.

29:41.060 --> 29:41.900
Yes.

29:49.430 --> 29:50.270
Wait here.

29:50.430 --> 29:51.270
Yes.

30:13.340 --> 30:14.475
How dare you devour spirits

30:14.486 --> 30:15.500
without permission?

30:20.470 --> 30:21.310
Jiang Ai.

30:36.990 --> 30:37.830
Your Ladyship.

30:39.300 --> 30:40.140
Your Ladyship.

30:42.300 --> 30:43.150
Your Ladyship,

30:43.150 --> 30:44.150
is something wrong?

30:44.870 --> 30:45.820
Shall I pursue him?

30:46.910 --> 30:47.950
He's jumped into the pool.

30:47.950 --> 30:48.790
How to pursue?

30:49.170 --> 30:50.160
By jumping in?

31:10.740 --> 31:13.380
(Yu)

31:21.907 --> 31:23.840
Why didn't the Lord
of Yuling Temple come today?

31:24.150 --> 31:24.990
He asked for leave?

31:30.990 --> 31:31.936
That doesn't seem right.

31:32.670 --> 31:34.100
The Lord of Yuling Temple

31:34.396 --> 31:35.550
has always upheld the rules.

31:36.060 --> 31:37.190
He never misses court.

31:46.540 --> 31:48.260
Greetings, Your Grace.

31:49.390 --> 31:51.090
The Lord of Yuling Temple
has met disaster

31:51.580 --> 31:52.710
and annihilation.

31:54.130 --> 31:54.990
This...

31:54.990 --> 31:55.801
It was so sudden.

31:55.812 --> 31:57.045
- What happened?
- Your Grace,

31:57.056 --> 31:57.780
even if he was

31:57.820 --> 31:58.910
as stubborn as a mule,

31:59.060 --> 32:00.060
you shouldn't have...

32:03.230 --> 32:04.580
After curfew,

32:05.190 --> 32:06.190
his Lord Token

32:06.190 --> 32:07.910
appeared before me out of nowhere.

32:08.430 --> 32:10.190
I traced the token's spirit power.

32:10.190 --> 32:11.580
It came from the Prison.

32:12.300 --> 32:13.630
When I went to look,

32:13.780 --> 32:15.430
there was no trace of him.

32:15.740 --> 32:17.020
Even Xusheng's memories

32:17.020 --> 32:18.190
were tampered with.

32:20.420 --> 32:21.260
(Yu)

32:21.260 --> 32:22.670
What happened can't be known.

32:24.230 --> 32:25.670
Even Xusheng was tampered with.

32:25.870 --> 32:26.910
Who could be that capable?

32:34.100 --> 32:36.260
You looked deep in thought just now.

32:37.570 --> 32:38.580
Do you have any leads?

32:40.390 --> 32:41.990
I am being punished for my offense.

32:42.190 --> 32:43.500
I have neither men nor power now.

32:43.740 --> 32:44.706
What leads could I have?

32:45.020 --> 32:46.390
I will surely follow Her Grace.

32:47.500 --> 32:49.020
From this day on, send more people

32:49.910 --> 32:51.060
to search the Void.

32:51.780 --> 32:52.670
Your Grace,

32:52.670 --> 32:54.150
who are we to investigate?

32:58.470 --> 32:59.710
Bai Sanxing.

33:00.300 --> 33:01.140
Bai...

33:02.100 --> 33:03.670
Bai Sanxing. Bai Sanxing.

33:03.820 --> 33:05.100
He still hasn't been annihilated?

33:06.430 --> 33:07.270
Well...

33:20.630 --> 33:21.938
Just now in the Sovereign's Hall,

33:21.949 --> 33:22.740
you told Her Grace

33:22.740 --> 33:24.910
you've never met Bai Sanxing.

33:25.990 --> 33:26.830
Why?

33:27.100 --> 33:28.230
Is there a problem?

33:30.060 --> 33:31.190
Let's put aside

33:31.190 --> 33:32.950
how Bai Sanxing

33:32.950 --> 33:33.843
got out of the Prison.

33:34.910 --> 33:36.100
I know Bai Sanxing well.

33:37.390 --> 33:39.150
You are the knot in his heart.

33:39.740 --> 33:41.740
He has loved you for a thousand years.

33:41.950 --> 33:43.300
He's always been unable to let go

33:43.300 --> 33:44.230
of your rejection.

33:44.500 --> 33:46.500
He's tried every way to claim you.

33:48.980 --> 33:49.860
300 years ago,

33:49.860 --> 33:51.410
you lured him into the Prison,

33:51.420 --> 33:53.540
and he wandered lost for centuries.

33:54.430 --> 33:56.150
After he escaped,

33:56.390 --> 33:57.950
how could he not come for you?

34:00.230 --> 34:01.340
He loves me?

34:01.780 --> 34:03.910
I'd say he wanted to master me.

34:04.300 --> 34:06.100
He always longs to claim

34:06.100 --> 34:07.580
anything fine in the world.

34:08.220 --> 34:09.750
Perhaps after he woke up,

34:09.750 --> 34:11.790
something else caught his fancy,

34:11.950 --> 34:13.750
so I was set aside for a while.

34:14.660 --> 34:16.270
But speaking of deceit,

34:16.870 --> 34:18.100
you are

34:18.100 --> 34:20.350
his most loyal Vice Lord.

34:21.180 --> 34:23.540
Now that he's escaped,

34:23.750 --> 34:26.620
shouldn't he settle with you first?

34:27.830 --> 34:28.910
Why did I just hear

34:28.910 --> 34:30.830
you tell Her Grace

34:31.350 --> 34:34.700
you'd never met Bai Sanxing?

34:44.390 --> 34:46.350
I've never met Bai Sanxing.

34:48.540 --> 34:50.540
Neither have I.

34:52.540 --> 34:54.540
Instead of doubting each other,

34:54.540 --> 34:57.020
best pray for yourself.

35:19.860 --> 35:22.860
(Nandu, Capital of Great Liang)

35:22.950 --> 35:23.830
The joy is shared.

35:23.830 --> 35:24.670
Rise.

35:24.690 --> 35:25.620
Congratulations.

35:25.750 --> 35:26.590
It was no easy feat.

35:27.220 --> 35:28.060
Mr. Liu.

35:28.790 --> 35:30.060
Mr. Liu.

35:31.060 --> 35:31.900
General Duan.

35:32.320 --> 35:34.150
General Duan, you've won great merit.

35:34.270 --> 35:35.850
His Majesty will reward you well.

35:36.060 --> 35:36.846
Congratulations.

35:36.910 --> 35:37.820
Congratulations.

35:37.870 --> 35:38.830
Thank you.

35:39.096 --> 35:40.129
Congratulations, Mr. Fang.

35:40.189 --> 35:41.310
Congratulations, Mr. Fang.

35:42.470 --> 35:43.310
Mr. Fang.

35:43.700 --> 35:45.580
Congratulations, Mr. Fang.

35:50.470 --> 35:51.350
Long time no see.

35:52.140 --> 35:53.390
You've risen fast

35:54.170 --> 35:55.890
and become the Vice Minister of Revenue.

35:56.350 --> 35:57.290
Congratulations.

35:59.380 --> 36:00.220
You are too kind.

36:01.060 --> 36:02.580
You turned the tide

36:03.180 --> 36:05.100
and led your troops
across the Guanhe River,

36:05.313 --> 36:06.506
storming the enemy camp alone,

36:06.740 --> 36:08.340
and taking Awo'erqi's head.

36:08.500 --> 36:09.460
Your merit is unmatched.

36:09.740 --> 36:11.340
His Majesty has summoned you

36:11.340 --> 36:12.340
back to report.

36:12.580 --> 36:13.780
A reward must surely follow.

36:14.060 --> 36:14.900
I offer

36:15.140 --> 36:16.740
my congratulations in advance.

36:16.740 --> 36:17.900
What great influence.

36:17.900 --> 36:18.740
Indeed.

36:21.460 --> 36:24.500
His Majesty arrives.

36:42.500 --> 36:44.180
Greetings, Your Majesty.

36:44.380 --> 36:48.060
Long live Your Majesty.

36:52.020 --> 36:52.900
My loyal ministers,

36:53.540 --> 36:54.380
rise.

36:55.020 --> 36:56.660
Thank you, Your Majesty.

36:57.340 --> 36:58.180
This time,

36:58.780 --> 37:00.026
in our battle with North Chong,

37:00.540 --> 37:01.980
we won a sweeping victory.

37:02.673 --> 37:03.919
For the first time in 30 years,

37:04.300 --> 37:06.020
we crossed the Guanhe River

37:06.500 --> 37:07.820
and reclaimed Shuozhou, Yunzhou,

37:07.820 --> 37:10.340
and Luozhou in one stroke.

37:10.940 --> 37:13.100
This is a great blessing
for Great Liang.

37:13.420 --> 37:14.900
Heaven blesses Great Liang.

37:15.060 --> 37:16.740
Congratulations, Your Majesty.

37:17.220 --> 37:19.100
Now that the army returns in triumph,

37:19.700 --> 37:21.100
rewards should be granted by merit.

37:22.740 --> 37:23.780
Where is Qin Huanda?

37:24.100 --> 37:25.500
I'm Qin Huanda.

37:25.780 --> 37:26.740
Greetings, Your Majesty.

37:26.940 --> 37:28.020
This time, Qin Huanda

37:28.020 --> 37:29.460
has rendered outstanding service.

37:30.140 --> 37:31.606
Reward him with 5,000 taels of silver

37:31.940 --> 37:33.100
and 5,000 bolts of silk.

37:33.500 --> 37:35.620
Further, grant him
the title Duke of Defense.

37:36.260 --> 37:37.100
The Ministry of War

37:37.420 --> 37:39.860
will reward the other generals.

37:40.780 --> 37:42.460
Thank you, Your Majesty, for your grace.

37:43.020 --> 37:45.120
The Ministry of Revenue
raised funds and provisions.

37:45.580 --> 37:46.420
Fang even went

37:46.660 --> 37:48.860
to deliver the supplies.

37:49.380 --> 37:50.366
All meritorious officials

37:50.900 --> 37:52.060
shall be duly rewarded.

37:52.460 --> 37:53.780
Thank you, Your Majesty.

37:55.980 --> 37:58.900
Duan Xu took Awo'erqi's head

37:59.660 --> 38:00.933
and should rank first in merit.

38:01.620 --> 38:02.740
But he defied orders

38:03.007 --> 38:04.653
and attacked Shuozhou
without permission,

38:04.820 --> 38:06.740
putting the city's troops and people

38:06.740 --> 38:07.660
in grave danger.

38:08.580 --> 38:09.873
His merit cancels out his fault.

38:10.420 --> 38:12.340
He is stripped of General Tabai

38:12.860 --> 38:13.700
and bestowed

38:14.020 --> 38:15.700
the post of Court Counselor.

38:27.220 --> 38:28.180
Thank you, Your Majesty.

38:37.041 --> 38:42.371
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

38:42.701 --> 38:46.951
♪Light encountered shadow♪

38:48.311 --> 38:53.681
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

38:53.981 --> 38:58.581
♪The unbreakable fate♪

38:59.671 --> 39:01.511
♪Suddenly cracked♪

39:13.721 --> 39:19.161
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

39:19.341 --> 39:23.671
♪Light encountered shadow♪

39:25.041 --> 39:30.431
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

39:30.661 --> 39:34.601
♪The unbreakable fate♪

39:36.371 --> 39:38.261
♪Suddenly cracked♪

39:40.921 --> 39:44.081
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

39:44.081 --> 39:46.611
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

39:46.611 --> 39:52.131
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

39:52.131 --> 39:55.371
♪Following fate's guidance♪

39:55.371 --> 40:00.231
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

40:00.571 --> 40:03.591
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

40:03.591 --> 40:06.411
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

40:06.671 --> 40:09.201
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

40:09.201 --> 40:14.621
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

40:14.791 --> 40:17.861
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

40:18.021 --> 40:22.921
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

40:23.131 --> 40:26.601
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
